verse.lines:
{lang-eng}There’s a wideness in God’s mercy,
Like the wideness of the sea;
There’s a kindness in His justice,
Which is more than liberty.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}There is welcome for the sinner,
And more graces for the good;
There is mercy with the Savior;
There is healing in His blood.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}There is plentiful redemption
In the blood that has been shed;
There is joy for all the members
In the sorrows of the Head.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}For the love of God is broader
Than the measure of our mind;
And the heart of the eternal
Is most wonderfully kind.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}If our love were but more simple,
We should take Him at His word;
And our lives would be all sunshine
In the sweetness of our Lord.{/lang-eng}
